| Command    | Description        | Example                     |
| ---------- | ------------------ | --------------------------- |
| `lsblk`    | List block devices | `lsblk`                     |
| `fdisk -l` | Show partitions    | `sudo fdisk -l`             |
| `mount`    | Mount drive        | `sudo mount /dev/sdb1 /mnt` |
| `umount`   | Unmount drive      | `sudo umount /mnt`          |
| `df`       | Disk space usage   | `df -h`                     |
